reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality product as shown in pictures.
reviews.reviewText: The assembly could be easier. It is very time-consuming. It is very straightforward and clear steps, just takes a good one hour to assemble by 1 person.I wish the back panel was in 2 parts, and not one single large piece. I wanna use it to hide wires, modem, and cables. That would require a partially open back for wires. Anyways, still a good product.
